{
  "stem": "13096.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was a general, because the commandant of the camp, it was just a small-- a small officer, whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he was one of the generals of the army of the Russian that he was, you know, for the Allied, you know, to-- to make this liberation of the camp.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he spoke to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And plus, beside him, there was a very important person in the camp who was a Frenchman.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was an important man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was Huberman, Huberman, the violinist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He also, you know, intervened-- you know, intervened for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he spoke to the commandant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Eventually, he let us in, because-- but at one condition.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When did this camp form, at the time, you know, there were many, many, many prisoners-- I mean, like you say, like us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But they were sick with-- with tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So they say, you will come in the camp at the condition you are going to nurse those people sick with tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we say, doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We lose-- we didn't know what if it was dangerous or not dangerous, but so long that they let us in, we say we would look after the tuberculosis people.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Don't worry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But after a day or two, there was another Frenchman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He went to speak-- you know, because he was a doctor in this hospital-- in this-- it was not hospital.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was not hospital.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was like a block of sick people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He went to speak to the commandant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He say, definitely, I'm not allowed, those girls, these girls to come and work in this tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
